Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算攻下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉德一战已经打完一个月了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到耗了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边境的格拉德和这次的罗杰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北部的要冲姑且拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁这段时间 对方正在把各地的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集到王都周边加强防御吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来不能一味蛮攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种战争要打到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能一直战斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道队兵十么会来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为调任命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个是上面···
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻说他无视上面的命令是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没跟休伊说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毫无根据的谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长在开战前接到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护要员和剿灭恐怖分子的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直在忠实执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会有传言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要当这种分队的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫「这种」？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷克一等兵曹长不以这支分队为豪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回想一下 皮尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一开始就给人感觉很讨厌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我们总感觉低人一等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我这种人是不会和你们待一间帐篷的」这种？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这种眼神···
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 上任都一个月了 我们一点都不了解队长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想把背后交给这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连莉莉二等兵曹都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯黛拉姐 你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡尔达斯州的最东面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有座叫阿萨利雅的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是领主统治的悠闲之地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听罗杰斯一战抓到的俘虏说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当地部队在据点里可能留有剩余物资
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能像上次那样 不但扑空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还造成无谓的战斗出现牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要侦查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说领主也带着总iSi防卫哈利安德了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的应该只有一些当地部队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入应该不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上 明早八点整出发 有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉比平时的轻松 那是最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休伊一等兵曹 说这种话的人一般死得最快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵达后 皮尔斯和布雷克在城区东侧驾驶神通待命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的人去摸清实地情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦查后 二十点整在这里集合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么偏僻的地方 东西倒是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然以前就知道生产力水平不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但亲眼见识后还是很受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件好像很适合斯黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟索莱伊想独吞这些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优姬·索莱伊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是个小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:06:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一定要杀了那个公主 你会怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 有命令就会下手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是粮仓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏是还看剩就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来果然已经搬走一批了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战况如此 很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他物资也很紧张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你别进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我们这就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们住在那边的管理楼里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理楼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在那里没人用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在那里生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你们是清洁工吧 怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识的人在这仓库里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里工作顺便看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃的昨天全搬走了哦 那人也一起走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该走了要是被骑士团发现会挨骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士团？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 毛里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 躲卡车里就不号谡骑士团发现了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粮仓里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清洁工 开卡车送了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粮仓怎么样 有东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有水果罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能带出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这个叔叔带出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫我爱吃甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你···
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且快过保质期了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其放到过期 不如拿来大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也分一点给孩子们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉娜也来吧一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别激动嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和大家一起吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫斯黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这娃娃真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸妈妈买给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很珍惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们都宕战争中死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里安全才送来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们 好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你们刚说的骑士团 是哈利安德骑士团吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔没在这里见过 他们一直在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那栋楼里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 是我们的老客人 得去打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是假设
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你现在觉得自己无处可归
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后一定会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系不上欧文斯特务少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长正在执行潜入任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在定时联络之前无法取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才有情报称 这里据点内有骑士团的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在调查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士团？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才哈利安德的侦察队发来报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称索莱伊军正在前往阿萨利雅 是大队规模
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大队吗 来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和骑士团说不定有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西是···
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型清澄的粮食生产设备？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一台驱动这么多设备吗 这是旧型号的几倍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王国军来这里 恐怕是为了把这些食粮送去前线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福利特参谋长 您怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:13:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前调配不到足够兵力迎击那支大队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖尔·欧文斯特务少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否赶在王国军到来之前拿到新型清澄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并破坏生产设备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到 但会殃及附近平民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 用这台新型清澄产出粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果普及到索莱伊全域 战况将明显不利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争持续时间越久对我国人民伤害越大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一 我们派两支炮兵中队12架机体赶过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的意思是···
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们如果失败
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将赶在敌军大队到达之前远程攻击生产设备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预测敌军大队将于三小时后抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我方炮兵中队的炮击 将于两小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两点三十分开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两小时？没疯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划边移动边说 虽然有没有都差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像都是战争遗孤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始潜入 照计划进行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始我单独行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们照计划夺取新型清澄 炸掉生产设备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理琐事 接下来由你负责指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没毛病吧 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 我们继续执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 从没听说过有这种队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先要让运行中的清澄停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要操作这里的终端 和清澄那里的终端
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 那边交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 二 一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 二 一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你···
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧让所有人集合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉 确定停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里也确定停了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯黛拉姐 后面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机正好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 大家抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边 不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 别过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把枪 和打死爸爸的人用的是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是格兰迪嘉的军人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你谨慎点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险这家伙疯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 皮尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 我们已拿到新型清澄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并已布置好炸药 你那边如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在管理楼门口 还没离开基地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续按计划执行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下生产设备爆破掉的话 这里所有人都活不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别爆破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在于什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上卡车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你们别爆破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拒绝一次 我杀一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么···
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐···
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你···
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都得死 不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我们撤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王军马上就会来 让他们保护你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为我们会谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就该去死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人犯 快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人犯···
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉娜 刚才是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把爸爸妈妈还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把家还给我 都还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在做的就是这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 你也能一直战斗下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才和他们聊过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但放弃任务 而且要是出人命了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任部下也是队长的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯黛拉怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你挺过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指什么 通宵的话打夜战的时候习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个任务什么时候来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了
